- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper evaluates the performance of cross-lingual word embeddings using a dataset and discusses the impact of dataset quality on the results. This involves machine learning techniques and hence, cs.LG is a likely sub-category. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper discusses the quality of a dataset used for intrinsic evaluation of cross-lingual word embeddings and its impact on the ranking of different systems. This involves information retrieval techniques and hence, cs.IR is a possible sub-category. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper deals with the evaluation of cross-lingual word embeddings and discusses the impact of dataset quality on the results. This involves AI techniques and hence, cs.AI is a possible sub-category.
